 4\,000 on delivery of a high-quality file of the finished film). No applic
 ation fee.\nDuration: Per documentary project\n\nMore: https://altercine.o
 rg/en/documentary-film-grants/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_m
