 und the transmediale festival)\; applicants must be Swiss or Switzerland-b
 ased\nAward: Two-month residency with an artist fee of CHF 2\,000 per mont
 h\, plus a CHF 15\,000 production grant for the selected project\, and tra
 vel and accommodation for the festival and residency. For duos or collecti
 ves the fee and grant remain the same and are shared. No application fee.\
 nDuration: Two-month residency\; selected project must be completed by Dec
 ember 2027\n\nMore: https://transmediale.de/en/news/digital-art-residency-
